		<h1 class="opener__hed   wp-block-post-title">Toxic Wastewater From Oil Fields Keeps Pouring Out of the Ground. Oklahoma Regulators Failed to Stop It.</h1>

			</div>
	
</div>


<div class="wp-block-group article-meta-1 article-meta-1--center is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow">
			<div class="article-meta-1__byline wp-block-propublica-byline">
	<span class="wp-block-propublica-byline-text">by </span><span class="wp-block-propublica-byline-profile"><a href="https://www.propublica.org/people/nick-bowlin">Nick Bowlin</a></span><span class="wp-block-propublica-byline-text">, </span><span class="wp-block-propublica-byline-organization"><a href="https://www.readfrontier.org/">The Frontier</a></span></div>


		<div class="article-meta-1__pubdate wp-block-post-date"><time datetime="2025-10-29T05:30:00-04:00">October 29, 2025, 5:30 am</time></div>
	
	
