oads/2025/10/GettyImages-2235473181_maxHeight_3000_maxWidth_3000.jpg?resize=527,351 527w, https://www.propublica.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/GettyImages-2235473181_maxHeight_3000_maxWidth_3000.jpg?resize=752,501 752w, https://www.propublica.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/GettyImages-2235473181_maxHeight_3000_maxWidth_3000.jpg?resize=1149,766 1149w, https://www.propublica.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/GettyImages-2235473181_maxHeight_3000_maxWidth_3000.jpg?resize=2000,1333 2000w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 422px) 100vw, 422px" /></a></figure>


